| TC ID  | Test Scenario                                         | Test Steps                                                                                            | Expected Result                                                         |
| ------ | ----------------------------------------------------- | ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ----------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| TC_001 | Verify user can launch the ParaBank application       | 1. Open browser.<br>2. Navigate to ParaBank URL.                                                      | ParaBank home page should load successfully.                            |
| TC_002 | Verify user can navigate to the registration page     | 1. Launch ParaBank application.<br>2. Click on the "Register" link.                                   | Registration page should be displayed successfully.                     |
| TC_003 | Verify user can register with valid details           | 1. Navigate to Registration page.<br>2. Enter valid user details.<br>3. Submit the registration form. | User account should be created successfully.                            |
| TC_004 | Verify successful account creation                    | 1. Complete registration process.<br>2. Observe registration confirmation page.                       | Successful account creation message should be displayed.                |
| TC_005 | Verify user can navigate to the Account Overview page | 1. Register successfully.<br>2. Navigate to Account Overview page.                                    | Account Overview page should be displayed.                              |
| TC_006 | Verify account balance is displayed after login       | 1. Open Account Overview page.<br>2. View account details section.                                    | Account balance should be displayed and available for logging/printing. |
